{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Void Echo is a psychological horror game that plunges players into the unsettling and surreal atmosphere of liminal spaces. Viewed through the grainy lens of an old camera, this first-person experience evokes a sense of isolation and unease as you explore vast, non-linear environments that seem both familiar and otherworldly. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In Void Echo, you are stranded in a world that feels trapped between reality and dreams, where each space hides secrets and fragmented memories of a forgotten past. Guided only by the flickering light of your flashlight, you must uncover hidden paths, solve environmental puzzles, and survive lurking threats to escape the eerie, dreamlike environments.</p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3304410?t=1737166308","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3304410?t=1737166308","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304410/495245a4070ef75b390ba676aa8217ba377ffb71/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737166308","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304410/495245a4070ef75b390ba676aa8217ba377ffb71/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737166308","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"demos":[{"appid":3439120,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Void Echo is a psychological horror game that plunges players into the unsettling and surreal atmosphere of liminal spaces. Viewed through the grainy lens of an old camera, this first-person experience evokes a sense of isolation and unease as you explore vast, non-linear environments that seem both familiar and otherworldly. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In Void Echo, you are stranded in a world that feels tra